column1: Bermula bulan rujukan Jun 2022, statistik tertentu telah disesuaikan selaras dengan penggunaan Harmonised Commodity description and Coding system 2022 (HS2022).
column20: Commencing on June 2022, some statistics has been realigned with regards to the adoption of Harmonised Commodity description and Coding system 2022 (HS2022).
